high_descs: Turn left into the room and go to the bed on the right.
Pick up the mug on the bed.
Leave the room take a left and then a right into the kitchen and go to the fridge.
Put the mug in the refrigerator and take the mug back out.
Turn left and there is a bookshelf on your right.
Put the mug on the lower shelf on the bookshelf on your right closest to the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled Mug on the Shelf

high_descs: Walk to the bedroom to your left, then hang a right and go to the bed.
Pick up the mug from the bed behind the tin can.
Turn around and walk to the doorway to your left and head towards the fridge.
Put the coffee mug into the fridge, wait for a moment and get the mug out of the fridge.
Head to the shelf to your left next to the fridge.
Put the mug on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a coffee mug from bedroom, put it on a shelf in the kitchen

high_descs: Turn around and go near the bed.
Take the mug from the bed
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the mug into the fridge.
Turn around and go near the shelf.
Put the mug on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Placed the mug on the shelf.
